## Development Workflow

1. Find or open an issue describing the change.
2. Branch from `[main]`: `[type/short-description]`.
3. Make the change. Keep it one logical change per PR.
4. Add or update tests. [Coverage expectation.]
5. Run the full local gate before pushing:
   ```bash
   [npm run lint]
   [npm test]
   ```
6. Open a PR (see below).

